      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northvolt将劳动力削减至1,700，作为破产过程的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/northvolt-cuts-workforce-to-1-700-as-part-of-bankruptcy-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产的电池制造商Northvolt AB将继续在瑞典运营1,700名员工，而其余员工将被解雇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/northvolt-cuts-workforce-to-1-700-as-part-of-bankruptcy-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
